                "invention-title": [
                    "Harsh-environment-resistant wall painting reinforcing agent and preparation method thereof",
                    "一种耐恶劣环境性壁画加固剂及其制备方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention relates to a harsh environment resistant mural reinforcing agent and a preparation method thereof. The reinforcing agent uses hydroxyl-containing acrylic resin as a main chain, and aromatic siloxane and fluorophenyl with low surface energy as durable and waterproof branched chains; the hydroxyl group, the aromatic ring group and the fluoro group in the structure respectively provide acting sites for hydrogen bonds, pi-pi stacking and fluorine-fluorine interaction. Strong cohesive energy is generated through pi-pi accumulation, hydrogen bonds and fluorine-fluorine interaction, so that the bonding strength can be kept lasting and stable. And compared with the existing reinforcing agent, the adhesive has the comprehensive advantages of lasting adhesive strength, excellent aging resistance, severe condition resistance, high permeability and the like. In addition, the reinforcing agent disclosed by the invention has hydrophilicity, so that the reinforcing agent can be better bonded with the wall painting; and meanwhile, the paint has hydrophobicity, and can effectively prevent water from damaging the mural cultural relics."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明涉及一种耐恶劣环境性壁画加固剂及其制备方法，本发明加固剂使用含羟基的丙烯酸树脂作为主链，低表面能的芳香族硅氧烷和氟苯基作为耐用且防水的支链，结构中的羟基、芳环和氟基基团分别为氢键、π‑π堆叠和氟‑氟相互作用提供了作用位点。通过π‑π堆积、氢键和氟‑氟相互作用产生强大的内聚能，使得粘接强度能够保持持久的稳定。而且与现有加固剂相比，具有持久粘接力、优异的耐老化性、耐恶劣条件性和高渗透性等综合优势。此外，本发明的加固剂具有亲水性，有利于与壁画更好地粘接；同时兼备疏水性，能有效防止水分对壁画文物造成破坏。"
                }
            ]
